pull_requests.title: Update AWS S3 bucket
pull_requests.body:
Hi, I was reading the AWS S3 bucket section and found some minor improvements:

* Renamed the directory/section to "AWS S3 Bucket", expanding AWS to Amazon Web Services, the old section name: Amazon Web Services Amazon Bucket S3, doesn't make a lot of sense. Technically it's also an S3 Bucket, therefore the name change too
* Fixed some grammar, and style issues from the guide

It's my first time contributing to this project, so I hope it meets the standards, else happy to address any concerns.
